<paragraph id="6A619C1A69F655BE32762ECF410C91E1" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Typification.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7C6660F089D9E4C086757587CBFECAE1" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">The lectotype in P-JUSS is not annotated by Choisy but is the only possible specimen that could be chosen as the type.</paragraph>
